data.description: Check out this beautiful and spacious home in Mill Valley neighborhood. The open floor plan has a bright and modern feel, a pergola covered deck and back yard are perfect for recreation and entertaining. Owner's suite with shower, soaking tub, and walk-in closet. Large landing area is perfect for a  home office or recreation area. Located on a quiet road with access to community pool!
